metadata.name: Meh #1
metadata.description:
The Mehtaverse is the genesis series of 2222 collectible NFTs by faith-based artist Patrick Bezalel.

The series of 2222 Meh (sheep) is more than an NFT art. It is a journey with the artist as he steps into this new space. By supporting this genesis series, we are committed to grant you access to special previews for collections and you will receive free NFT mints quarterly.
